mk.tmdb.entity.person

Class TMDbPerson

  • java.lang.Object
    • mk.tmdb.entity.TMDbEntity
      • mk.tmdb.entity.person.TMDbPersonThumbnail
        • mk.tmdb.entity.person.TMDbPerson
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TMDbPersonFull

    public class TMDbPerson
extends TMDbPersonThumbnail
    Class that represents a person with limited features.
    Person class has more features than PersonThumbnail class.
    To get a more detailed class see TMDbPersonFull.
    Author:
    Mirko Polato
